<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kumpi muol a liem ding kuon in, lunghel a kaitho sek,
 Ngailo leh lawp lo him him a um puoi;
 I ngaih Kristmas ni eng a hung suok kit ta ie,
 Hung hawih zaw diek hen Bethlehem pak tawh;
 A hung pak kit tai pak bang I lawm.

[V2]
 Aw a hawih ngei ie,
 Zie ni kipah um chawm cha hi,
 I vang nei ngei ie, kipahni I tungkit tai,
 Lungguol takin lawp in zaila sai tiu;
 I lungkham nau puon bang lipthai tiu.

[V3]
 2. Thawmhaute leh lusun chate chantawk hi ngaihtuoh tie,
 Nung sul muolliem nung ngaiin a kap ui
 Pak bang a lawp uh zie ni lopi hungtun hin;
 In kuon kima lenlai kha ngai diek in,
 Kap in luonthi puon bang hui in au.

[V4]
 3. Gam vangla a guol ngaihte damin na um nau em?
 Kristmas ni kipah um I tungkit tau;
 Chung Pathien in dam takin ei veng chiet u hen;
 Damtakin aw, I kituok kit mau cheng;
 Kipak in lasa'n chibai mangpha.

[V5]
 4. Chung Pathien in ei veng zel hen, kipakin la saitiu.
 A suihlung hel cheng le dam tau hen;
 I ngak ni kipah um I tung kit tau e;
 I puokgik cheng cheng uh chuh paihthai tiu;
 Lawpin hunpha I neih sung uhin.</lyrics>
<title>Kristmas Ni Vak</title>
</song>